{"tid":1549843,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［突發！］青年持有長者八達通 被黑警指盜竊","createTime":"2019-09-07T12:58:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T16:20:21.000Z","uid":262146,"like":26,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"9b739e4c6dadaa1bda138e7e33fc5b266e383c7b","tid":1549843,"uid":262146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:58:08.000Z","msg":"青年藏長者八達通疑盜竊　警帶走調查<br />\n<br />\n防暴警察搜查期間，發現一名姓李的年青男子身上藏有長者八達通，懷疑他涉嫌盜竊。警員隨即查問：「點解你有長者八達通？」李男回答指：「我唔需要解釋」，並稱該張八達通於半小時前在香港站買。警方其後檢查該男子的隨身物品，發現袋中有救護用品、繃帶紗布、消毒藥水及N95口罩。該名男子在場高叫自己姓名、身分證號碼，聲稱自己為公開大學護理系三年級學生，並叫現場人士代為找星火幫手。李男其後被警方拘捕，並押上警車。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/突發/372729/9-7機場-裝甲車泊收費亭-護理系學生有長者八達通-紗布被捕\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC%2F372729%2F9-7%E6%A9%9F%E5%A0%B4-%E8%A3%9D%E7%94%B2%E8%BB%8A%E6%B3%8A%E6%94%B6%E8%B2%BB%E4%BA%AD-%E8%AD%B7%E7%90%86%E7%B3%BB%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%9C%89%E9%95%B7%E8%80%85%E5%85%AB%E9%81%94%E9%80%9A-%E7%B4%97%E5%B8%83%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95&d=59R0jsXjdYUW2Qgfgwt6uNUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=8dfdb262\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/突發/372729/9-7機場-裝甲車泊收費亭-護理系學生有長者八達通-紗布被捕</a>"},{"pid":"e2df63181b2b4820a472913646c6b1cb9e4c1134","tid":1549843,"uid":262146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:59:59.000Z","msg":"希望大家幫手推！！"},{"pid":"420b326e393759b99121a4bda24f99a7722fbf94","tid":1549843,"uid":67223,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T13:05:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3ioNHVB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3ioNHVB.jpg&h=320a7ea9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"55690eaba41341ab4da9cd877105a95aed11a465","tid":1549843,"uid":263367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T13:07:53.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f8fb111cfccec90ca0c888f9f5776eaa64a7b758","tid":1549843,"uid":262146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-09-07